1
00:00:09,560 --> 00:00:10,640
I often wonder

2
00:00:11,400 --> 00:00:13,839
why those pretty girls win at life

3
00:00:14,480 --> 00:00:15,240
What gives them the right?

4
00:00:16,399 --> 00:00:17,600
Just because of their face?

5
00:00:19,039 --> 00:00:20,359
And if they lost that face,

6
00:00:21,039 --> 00:00:22,320
would they still be loved?

7
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:35,560
What are you doing?

8
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:39,320
What are you doing?

9
00:00:41,159 --> 00:00:41,640
Get away!

10
00:01:11,359 --> 00:01:12,200
Is this person you?

11
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,200
Whether you believe it or not,

12
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:21,280
I never once thought of killing anyone.

13
00:01:22,239 --> 00:01:23,680
She kept hitting me.

14
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:25,640
I had no choice but to fight back.

15
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:26,840
After she passed out,

16
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,280
I looked at her face

17
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:29,840
and I wanted her to taste

18
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:31,799
what it's like to be ugly.

19
00:01:32,439 --> 00:01:33,439
Who would've thought,

20
00:01:33,959 --> 00:01:35,040
she lost her footing

21
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:37,040
and drowned in the river.

22
00:01:38,519 --> 00:01:39,799
That was her karma.

23
00:01:40,799 --> 00:01:41,519
And after that?

24
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,840
Why did you keep killing?

25
00:01:44,799 --> 00:01:46,319
They wouldn't let me go.

26
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,359
Cindy is dead.

27
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,280
Did you know?

28
00:02:07,719 --> 00:02:08,639
Take it easy.

29
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,520
Have some water first.

30
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:18,759
Say something!

31
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,759
Did you do it?

32
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,080
I had no grudge against her.

33
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,000
Why would I kill her?

34
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:26,560
Cut the crap.

35
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,039
You were the one who envied her most.

36
00:02:28,439 --> 00:02:28,919
I...

37
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:33,840
Zhao Yan,

38
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,680
I gave you everything.

39
00:02:37,479 --> 00:02:39,120
How could I ever lie to you?

40
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:42,479
I love you so much.

41
00:02:44,439 --> 00:02:45,199
That face of yours...

42
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:46,639
With some makeup,

43
00:02:47,479 --> 00:02:48,719
it's at least presentable.

44
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:51,120
Do you love me?

45
00:02:51,719 --> 00:02:52,199
Yes.

46
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:53,639
Of course I do.

47
00:02:54,879 --> 00:02:55,680
I love you too.

48
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,719
Where's your tattoo?

49
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:26,800
Tattoo?

50
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,280
I'll get one for you.

51
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,879
What are you thinking?

52
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,520
Didn't you say you loved me?

53
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,159
I love plenty of people.

54
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,000
As if you deserve it.

55
00:03:42,719 --> 00:03:43,719
Liar!

56
00:03:44,439 --> 00:03:45,000
You...

57
00:03:47,199 --> 00:03:47,680
You...

58
00:04:16,639 --> 00:04:17,240
Fanny!

59
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,079
It was Lele!

60
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:20,000
It was Lele!

61
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:21,600
It was Lele!

62
00:04:21,759 --> 00:04:22,519
Come save me!

63
00:04:25,959 --> 00:04:26,800
Lele...

64
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,240
Take me to the hospital.

65
00:04:28,759 --> 00:04:29,560
I'm begging you.

66
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:30,720
Lele...

67
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:36,800
Lele...

68
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,240
Let me go.

69
00:04:38,839 --> 00:04:39,800
It's all my fault.

70
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,279
Lele, don't!

71
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:42,839
Don't kill me!

72
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:44,439
Lele, I'll marry you!

73
00:04:46,199 --> 00:04:46,680
Lele...

74
00:04:58,759 --> 00:04:59,439
Lele...

75
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,120
I'll marry you.

76
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,399
I truly love you.

77
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,959
The final step of making a mummy

78
00:05:05,959 --> 00:05:07,720
is wrapping the body in linen,

79
00:05:07,959 --> 00:05:09,720
applying spices on every layer.

80
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,480
Through this intricate process,

81
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,120
the flesh transcends time,

82
00:05:13,399 --> 00:05:14,720
becoming a silent witness linking

83
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,399
the mortal world to eternity.

84
00:05:20,439 --> 00:05:21,079
Lying to me?

85
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:21,839
No.

86
00:05:22,439 --> 00:05:23,199
I'm not lying to you.

87
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:25,680
I...

88
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:06,160
Zhao Yan died right here.

89
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,160
You don't need to look at me like that.

90
00:07:21,639 --> 00:07:22,800
I don't need pity.

91
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:25,360
Since he said he'd marry me,

92
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:29,240
he should keep his promise.

93
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:31,319
In life and death, together.

94
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,079
What about Fanny then?

95
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,079
Hey.

96
00:07:47,279 --> 00:07:47,920
Where are you?

97
00:07:50,279 --> 00:07:51,240
I know you did it.

98
00:07:52,399 --> 00:07:53,319
If you don't pay up,

99
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,079
I'll report you.

100
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,399
Where's the money?

101
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:07,040
All my money is here.

102
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:08,959
Can you let me go?

103
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,319
This is only for this month.

104
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,800
Next month, same again.

105
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,759
Or I'll tell the police

106
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:24,399
that you and Yu Tianfang

107
00:08:24,879 --> 00:08:26,120
conspired to kill Zhao Yan.

108
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:53,159
Why are you pushing me?

109
00:08:54,159 --> 00:08:55,000
Why?

110
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,559
Why?

111
00:09:14,039 --> 00:09:15,919
I love the Bai brothers' story.

112
00:09:16,279 --> 00:09:17,360
So I used Fanny

113
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:20,080
to put together a family portrait.

114
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,360
Right here,

115
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,240
I attacked Fanny.

116
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:31,679
The hospital called. Fanny's awake.

117
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,480
We did a brief interview with her.

118
00:09:34,559 --> 00:09:35,679
She identified the attacker.

119
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,120
It's Mao Lele.

120
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,120
My only regret

121
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,240
is dragging Brother Tianfang down.

122
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:44,720
He was so good to me.

123
00:09:45,639 --> 00:09:46,159
What a shame.

124
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,960
I'll never get the chance to repay him.

125
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,320
Brother Tianfang.

126
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,080
I'm sorry.

127
00:09:56,399 --> 00:09:58,279
Could you grab me a drink?

128
00:10:03,799 --> 00:10:04,600
What do you want?

129
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:05,679
Coke.

130
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,159
Sugar-free, please.

131
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:12,919
Did you get all that down?

132
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:14,879
Take her away.

133
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:41,480
Lele. Brother Tianfang.

134
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,720
Why are you so foolish?

135
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:47,159
I'm sorry, brother.

136
00:10:47,399 --> 00:10:49,039
Why didn't you tell me sooner?

137
00:10:49,039 --> 00:10:50,200
There might've been a way out.

138
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,440
Why did you do something so stupid?

139
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:53,559
I was afraid you'd worry about me.

140
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,480
I was afraid you'd hate me.

141
00:10:56,159 --> 00:10:58,240
Then I'd truly have nothing left.

142
00:11:01,399 --> 00:11:02,720
Say what you have to say, quickly.

143
00:11:03,279 --> 00:11:04,039
Keep an eye on her.

144
00:11:07,279 --> 00:11:07,879
Brother.

145
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,360
Your favorite Coke.

146
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,039
From now on,

147
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:13,600
I can't run out and get drinks for you anymore.

148
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:21,600
It's good.

149
00:11:23,679 --> 00:11:24,879
From now on, every time

150
00:11:25,159 --> 00:11:26,960
I drink Coke, I'll think of you.

151
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,759
I'll think of a girl

152
00:11:29,879 --> 00:11:31,080
named Mao Lele.

153
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,399
I'll never forget you.

154
00:11:35,039 --> 00:11:35,559
Brother.

155
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,799
If we could start over,

156
00:11:38,679 --> 00:11:40,039
would you like me?

157
00:11:45,639 --> 00:11:46,320
You

158
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:49,320
love eating really sour green apples.

159
00:11:50,399 --> 00:11:51,360
Every time

160
00:11:51,519 --> 00:11:54,240
you go out, you carry a little notebook to draw.

161
00:11:55,159 --> 00:11:56,919
You also sneak out back

162
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:58,240
to feed the stray cats.

163
00:12:01,159 --> 00:12:02,480
You don't like makeup or dressing up,

164
00:12:03,039 --> 00:12:04,759
because you want to be your true self.

165
00:12:05,639 --> 00:12:07,039
I like a girl just like you.

166
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:09,639
Like a little sister.

167
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:14,120
Thank you for not lying to me.

168
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:15,759
Brother.

169
00:12:16,879 --> 00:12:17,720
I'm leaving now.

170
00:12:20,279 --> 00:12:21,840
Take good care of yourself.

171
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:23,919
In my next life,

172
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,799
I'll definitely be braver.

173
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:26,799
Mao Lele.

174
00:12:27,879 --> 00:12:29,080
Remember to eat your meals on time.

175
00:12:52,799 --> 00:12:53,360
Captain Chu.

176
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:54,200
Let's go.

177
00:12:56,799 --> 00:12:57,600
Those two people...

178
00:12:57,759 --> 00:12:58,840
they looked kind of familiar.

179
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:04,039
That girl looked so pitiful.

180
00:13:05,399 --> 00:13:07,120
She must've been through a lot.

181
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:10,960
What's there to pity about a killer?

182
00:13:11,399 --> 00:13:13,480
She brought it on herself.

183
00:13:15,279 --> 00:13:16,279
Then what about us?

184
00:13:18,879 --> 00:13:20,200
You're picking a fight, aren't you?

185
00:13:20,559 --> 00:13:22,399
I told you, don't stay here.

186
00:13:22,399 --> 00:13:23,879
Don't stay here.

187
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:25,240
But you insisted on staying.

188
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,200
Now look what happened.

189
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:27,720
We ran into a murder case.

190
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:29,799
And we can't even leave.

191
00:13:30,159 --> 00:13:31,200
This month's money...

192
00:13:32,519 --> 00:13:33,600
we can't pay it back again.

193
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:37,399
If you hadn't gambled away even your shorts,

194
00:13:37,639 --> 00:13:39,679
would I be out scamming people with you every day?

195
00:13:39,679 --> 00:13:41,679
Living in fear all day long.

196
00:13:41,679 --> 00:13:42,600
If I'd known,

197
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:44,279
I'd have married that rich guy chasing me.

198
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:48,240
Don't you dare.

199
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:49,519
Don't you dare!

200
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:51,240
You hit me?

201
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:53,759
Screw you!

202
00:13:56,519 --> 00:13:57,200
Go on, hit me!

203
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:59,200
Beat me to death if you've got the guts!

204
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:01,039
I'll beat you to death today!

205
00:14:01,879 --> 00:14:02,759
That'll teach you to keep talking!

206
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,279
You want another man?

207
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:10,600
I was such a fool.

208
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:13,200
Lele's been through so much,

209
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:15,679
yet I didn't notice a thing.

210
00:14:16,039 --> 00:14:17,120
I sensed something was wrong,

211
00:14:17,879 --> 00:14:19,279
but I couldn't help.

212
00:14:20,519 --> 00:14:21,399
I'm partly to blame too.

213
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:23,759
No use overthinking it.

214
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:25,519
Just work hard from now on,

215
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:27,759
boost the performance numbers,

216
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:29,039
that's what matters most.

217
00:14:29,399 --> 00:14:30,279
Money, money, money.

218
00:14:30,279 --> 00:14:31,240
All you see is money.

219
00:14:31,679 --> 00:14:32,320
Qibao.

220
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:35,200
Don't talk to Boss Bai like that.

221
00:14:35,399 --> 00:14:36,879
We're not running a charity, are we?

222
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:39,159
What do you know?

223
00:14:39,879 --> 00:14:41,159
Okay, okay, my bad.

224
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:43,840
Hello, you two.

225
00:14:43,919 --> 00:14:45,480
Welcome to Qingyuan Villa.

226
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:46,679
Who made the reservation?

227
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:47,720
Under my name.

228
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:49,399
Wang Kechen.

229
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:50,919
Alright, here you go, sir.

230
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:51,759
I'll handle it.

231
00:14:54,159 --> 00:14:54,759
Fanny.

232
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:02,519
I'll go check in first.

233
00:15:03,159 --> 00:15:04,519
Lao Li, take care of them.

234
00:15:07,559 --> 00:15:08,159
This way, please.

235
00:15:08,799 --> 00:15:09,440
Hello.

236
00:15:09,799 --> 00:15:10,480
Wang Kechen.

237
00:15:13,799 --> 00:15:14,919
Quit rushing me.

238
00:15:14,919 --> 00:15:16,360
What's the rush? What is it?

239
00:15:19,279 --> 00:15:19,879
Brother Jun.

240
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:21,639
Brother Jun, what brings you here?

241
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:33,559
Boss.

242
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:36,159
Your favorite coffee.

243
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:40,919
What did you call me here for?

244
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:42,440
Tianfang.

245
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:45,080
I know you like He Siqi.

246
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:46,519
But a man

247
00:15:46,799 --> 00:15:48,240
should put his career first.

248
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:49,159
Only with a career

249
00:15:49,559 --> 00:15:50,399
can you truly protect

250
00:15:50,399 --> 00:15:52,000
the woman you love.

251
00:15:52,639 --> 00:15:53,679
Don't worry, boss.

252
00:15:53,840 --> 00:15:55,679
I always separate work from personal life.

253
00:15:55,679 --> 00:15:57,240
Personal romantic matters

254
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:58,200
will absolutely not affect

255
00:15:58,200 --> 00:15:59,759
my professionalism or focus at work.

256
00:16:00,399 --> 00:16:01,080
Do you know

257
00:16:01,279 --> 00:16:03,799
what kind of man women hate most?

258
00:16:06,559 --> 00:16:08,519
A wishy-washy man.

259
00:16:10,559 --> 00:16:11,000
Boss.

260
00:16:11,759 --> 00:16:13,080
Just say what you mean.

261
00:16:20,240 --> 00:16:21,879
There've been many incidents at the resort lately.

262
00:16:22,039 --> 00:16:23,320
You'd better keep a close eye on things.

263
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:26,320
Is that all?

264
00:16:26,519 --> 00:16:28,000
Isn't that exactly my job?

265
00:16:28,159 --> 00:16:29,080
Don't worry, boss.

266
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:37,000
From now on,

267
00:16:37,399 --> 00:16:38,960
you're the general manager here.

268
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:41,159
General manager?

269
00:16:42,240 --> 00:16:43,679
Can I really do it?

270
00:16:44,639 --> 00:16:45,840
Am... am I the right fit?

271
00:16:46,879 --> 00:16:48,120
I wouldn't have guessed.

272
00:16:48,360 --> 00:16:49,600
You really know how to play coy.

273
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:51,960
Whether you can handle it or not,

274
00:16:52,559 --> 00:16:54,000
right now the only person I can use

275
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:55,000
is you.

276
00:16:55,879 --> 00:16:56,720
If you screw it up,

277
00:16:57,159 --> 00:16:57,879
you're out immediately.

278
00:16:58,559 --> 00:16:59,120
I can do it.

279
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:00,559
I can do it, I can do it.

280
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:01,399
Thank you, boss.

281
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:02,200
Don't worry.

282
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,960
I won't let you down.

283
00:17:04,200 --> 00:17:05,799
I'll definitely run the resort well.

284
00:17:09,559 --> 00:17:10,240
Sorry about that.

285
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:11,640
Boss.

286
00:17:12,079 --> 00:17:14,079
You're really making that kid Yu Tianfang

287
00:17:14,440 --> 00:17:15,319
the general manager?

288
00:17:15,720 --> 00:17:16,440
Hey, Old Li.

289
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:17,720
Are you jealous of me or what?

290
00:17:18,079 --> 00:17:19,440
A man of your age,

291
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:21,039
still eavesdropping on people?

292
00:17:21,039 --> 00:17:21,559
Aren't you?

293
